- **Drug Type**: In terms of drug type, the market for penile cancer treatment can be classified into cytotoxic drugs, immunotherapeutic drugs, and targeted therapy drugs. These drugs are designed to target cancer cells and inhibit their growth, thereby improving patient outcomes and quality of life.

